steps.name: I click shopping cart on the homepage
I enter a discount coupon code "TUBE"
I click on Apply coupon button
I tick Agree with Terms and Conditions checkbox
I click on Checkout as guest button
I click on continue button on Billing address page
I click on continue button on Shipping method page
I click on continue button on Payment method page
I click on continue button on Payment information page
I click on confirm button on Confirm order page
Verify that the order is successfully processed
I click on continue button order completion page
